### Build tool (ie. output of `mvnw --version` or `gradlew --version`)

_No response_

### Additional information

Note that this issue is very similar to https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/34432 but for Hibernate Reactive. We fixed this issue by adding the `@WithSessionOnDemand` annotation at the class level of the auto-generated resource. 

Unfortunately, we cannot do the same for Hibernate ORM since adding the `@Transactional` annotation at the class level would imply all the methods require a transaction.
